El Jadida Horse Show
The El Jadida Horse Show is one of the most prominent annual events in Morocco, celebrating traditional equestrian arts like Tbourida. This exhibition brings together horse enthusiasts from around the world to showcase their riding skills and traditional horsemanship. It also serves as an opportunity to highlight Morocco's rich heritage in horse breeding and equestrian performance.
